# fields.prompt

**Fields for herobanner**:
1. `selectableVariant` (string) - "default" or "xDemo"
2. `title` (string)
3. `subtitle` (string)
4. `image` (image) - local file upload
5. `altText` (string)
6. `button` (heroButton) - link & label
7. `sortOrder` (number)
8. `globalComponentSource` (reference) - optional global reusability